#ground
  .container
    h2(style='color:white; font-size: 40px;') Media Pack
#underground
  .container.large
    div(style='display: flex;')
      div(style='flex:1')
        div(style='margin-top: 20px')
          h5 Developers:
          // Thanks https://thunderlotusgames.com/media-packs/ for the reference
          p(style='font-size: 100%;margin-top: 0.2em')
            a(href='https://orta.io') Orta Therox
            | and 
            a(href='https://lazerwalker.com') Em Lazer-Walker
          h5 Contributors:
          p(style='font-size: 100%;margin-top: 0.2em')
            a(href='http://stfj.net/') Zach Gage
          h5 Expected release:
          p(style='font-size: 100%;margin-top: 0.2em') July 2019
          h5 Platforms:
          p(style='font-size: 100%;margin-top: 0.2em') Android, iOS and a Web Demo
          h5 Press / Business Contact:
          p(style='font-size: 100%;margin-top: 0.2em')
            a(style='color: #be966e;text-decoration: none', href='mailto:team@flappyroyale.io') team@flappyroyale.io
      div(style='flex:1;padding: 10px;')
        p
          strong Flappy Royale
          |  is a battle royale-styled game influenced by Flappy Bird. It
          |  takes the competitive nature of a battle royale where far too many people play at once, with
          |  the un-forgiving nature of flappy games.
        p
          | Flappy Royale has two game modes: a royale free-for-all with up to 100 players and a daily
          | top-score system to see who got past the most pipes daily where players have a limited
          | number of tries.
        p
          | If it flaps (and kinda if it doesn&apos;t), we&apos;ve tried to get it in the game, giving you the
          | chance to play as all sorts of animals and glammed to the brim.
        p
          | We think you&apos;ll find it messy, frustrating, and very fun for 10 seconds. Then you hit a
          | pipe, and start all over again. You know the drill.
