    div
      h2 About the devs
      div(style='display: flex;')
        div(style='flex:1;padding-right: 20px;')
          p
            strong Orta
            |  is an engineer with a
            a(href='https://open.nytimes.com/five-questions-with-orta-therox-d5bb9659c50b') long experience
            | in the Open Source world, having built many tools used by the iOS and JavaScript
            | developer communities.
          p
            | Today he works on the
            a(href='https://artsy.github.io/blog/2019/04/05/omakase-typescript/') TypeScript programming language
            | at Microsoft. That&apos;s the language this game is created with.

        div(style='flex:1;color:#fff; ')
          p
            strong Em
            |  make experimental games, interactive art, and software tools.
          p
            | Her installations, artgames, and research projects have been featured in places such as
            | NPR&apos;s All Things Considered, the Venice Biennale, and the Smithsonian American Art
            | Museum.
